  "items": [
    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/mystery-man.svg",
      "name": "All Must Serve",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A living creature remains in area C6 for more than 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A ghostly servant attempts to enter the body of a random living creature in the room. The target must attempt a save against the ghostly servant's suggestion (@Check[type:will|dc:30] save) to head out into the castle to clean a randomly determined room on the second floor. A character attacked along the way can fight back, but once a battle is completed must return to the task at hand. Characters prevented from following the suggestion do not resist violently, but do seek to obey the suggestion to the best of their abilities until the duration expires or the effect is dispelled. The haunt then rolls intiative.</p>"
        },
